{"type":null,"faqId":37050,"title":"华为智能手环TalkBand B2的待机时间和使用时间是多少？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">   </span><span>蓝牙连接手机，以运动健康为主要使用场景，轻度使用的情况下待机约4-5天；重度使用约1-2天，例如电话每天超过4小时，经常用耳机听微信，听音乐等。电池的使用时间与用户使用手环的频度和场景息息相关。华为手环较普通的蓝牙耳机多了屏幕显示且又支持运动健康等统计，但我们手环理论通话时间约6小时，较市面上普通蓝牙耳机通话时间都长。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":1,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2214","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750140000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":95,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,待机时间,使用时间,电量,低电量,低电量提醒","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}